title: Ricky Singh from Backtrack

description:
Episode 287 - Welcome to 2018 and hope it’s going well for you. We have Ricky Signh who plays guitar in Backtrack on the show this week talking about growing up as a first generation immigrant, the music business and being open minded. I had such a positive conversation with him that I figured, what better way to ring in the new year on this front. Enjoy! Get 15% off by using the code PC100WORDSORLESS. Visit our friends over at No Echo for great features on punk, hardcore and all things heavy.
